cs.LO, cs.FL, cs.DS, cs.PL, cs.CC 

Reasoning: The paper deals with the formal language and automata theory, specifically higher-order counter automata. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also discusses the complexity of reachability analysis, which falls under the category of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity). The transfer of results to the formal language setting makes cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) a likely category as well. Finally, the paper discusses the hierarchy of languages, which falls under the category of cs.PL (Programming Languages).
